      "id": "spn_surveillance_population",
      "short_name": "ABCs surveillance population",
      "long_name": "ABCs pneumococcal surveillance population",
      "category": "Respiratory diseases",
      "short_description": "Total population under active surveillance for invasive pneumococcal disease in the ABCs catchment area",
      "long_description": "The number of persons living within the ABCs catchment area for pneumococcal disease surveillance in a given year. Catchment areas vary by state and over time as surveillance regions have expanded. The national total reflects the sum across the 8 sites that consistently report to ABCs (CA, CT, GA, MD, MN, NY, OR, TN).",
